column5: I finally got around to uploading a few pictures into my gallery so now I thought I'd see if I can figure out how to post them.  It sure does take a while on dial up though  My boys, well sort of...this is my nepwhew Rob who is staying with me, and his son Ryan....closest I'll get to a son and grandson    This is the little guy being too cute, he'll be coming to visit this weekend    This is Austin, the fence is 5ft high so that will give you an idea of how much snow we have here.    Now all I have to do is work on my resizing skills to get rid of the graininess in the pictures.  Maureen
Cool, parcel's going in tomorrows mail Maureen.
Wow...those fish look remarkably like children!! Where did you catch them??? LOL....  Great pics...very cute!
HMMMMM................Austin........................ a better name could not be spoken,
Very nice Maureen.  Yep, his son is a cutie like you said at the swill.  Joey
